of the Declaration"

248
00:13:13,720 --> 00:13:16,640
"and destroy the remaining structure
of the Constitution",

249
00:13:16,720 --> 00:13:20,160
which it just isn't. It isn't that.

250
00:13:20,440 --> 00:13:22,640
But in the wake
of the George Floyd protests,

251
00:13:22,760 --> 00:13:26,320
