267
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:16,720
she was right not to do it.
No big loss.

268
00:14:17,120 --> 00:14:19,360
Because Mark Meadows,
Trump's chief of staff,

269
00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:21,760
has since revealed President Trump
saw that interview,

270
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:24,760
and when Rufo said, "I call on the
