287
00:15:18,400 --> 00:15:21,160
And he's openly admitted
that he's been engaged

288
00:15:21,280 --> 00:15:23,560
in a deliberate branding exercise,

289
00:15:23,640 --> 00:15:28,000
tweeting, "we have successfully frozen
their brand, critical race theory,"

290
00:15:28,120 --> 00:15:29,760
"into the public conversation"

291
00:15:29,840 --> 00:15:32,400
"and are steadily driving up
negative perceptions".

292
00:15:32,520 --> 00:15:35,880
"The goal is to have the public read
something crazy in the newspaper"

293
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:38,640
"and immediately think
critical race theory".

294
00:15:38,920 --> 00:15:41,680
And the thing is,
it fucking worked.

295
00:15:41,840 --> 00:15:44,640
Because whenever you hear CRT now,

296
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:47,680
