00:33:35,400 --> 00:33:39,760
Because for generation after generation,
we've told school kids fairy tales

631
00:33:39,880 --> 00:33:41,360
about race in this country.

632
00:33:41,440 --> 00:33:44,000
And maybe it's time
we stop doing that.

633
00:33:44,120 --> 00:33:47,480
